com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors

Interface Summary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service, SummaryTypes
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SummaryStub

    public interface Summary
extends Service, SummaryTypes

    The Summary interface provides methods to retrieve the current states of Supervisors.

    Only the basic information of the given Supervisor is being queried.

    . This interface was added in vSphere API 8.0.0.1.
